60245.display: A card from U-96. It reads: "Time flies, eh? Still remember the day I came here like it was yesterday, 'cept I've made tons of friends and memories since then. This year's been great so far and it's only gonna get better! Right, Commander?"
60245.name: U-96's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60246.display: A card from Essex. It reads: "Happy anniversary, Commander. How many years at this port does that make it now? It feels like we've known each other practically forever... I dare say that's a bit mysterious. Maybe this is a case for Detective Ess– Err, I mean, Detective Bristol!"
60246.name: Essex's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60247.display: A card from Enterprise. It reads: "Happy anniversary, Commander. It's been a real journey getting to where we are now, and there's still a long road ahead of us. Hope I can be with you every step of the way."
60247.name: Enterprise's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60248.display: A card from Hood. It reads: "My, it's been really hot lately, hasn't it? Not just the weather, but the passions in all our hearts. After all, who wouldn't be excited to celebrate another anniversary with all their friends? Here's to a continued splendid year, Commander."
60248.name: Hood's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60249.display: A card from Yukikaze. It reads: "Le Malin thought she could draw a better straw than Yukikaze the Great! What a moron! Listen, Commander, this is an occasion to celebrate, so I'm going to give you my blessing of luck! Make the most of it while it lasts~"
60249.name: Yukikaze's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60250.display: A card from Montpelier. It reads: "Crazy how much has changed in one year and how much has stayed the same. I've gotten closer to Cleve, hung out with friends, celebrated holidays... In a way it's been like any other year, but fresh in some way. Anyway, happy anniversary, Commander."
60250.name: Montpelier's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60251.display: A card from Swiftsure. It reads: "I've never felt quite sure I'm celebrating the port's anniversary right. Sure, I can dance decently, strike up conversations, and just have fun, but... I don't know, it feels like something's missing. Maybe I'm just being weird. At any rate, happy anniversary, Commander!"
60251.name: Swiftsure's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60252.display: A card from Le Malin. It reads: "Ugghhh... I'm gonna melt like ice cream in this heat... Can I really not get one of my sisters to fill in for me? I'll be with you in spirit, celebrating from the comfort of my air-conditioned room, I promise..."
60252.name: Le Malin's Gift (4th Anniversary)

60415.display: A card from Richelieu. It reads: "I wish you a pleasant anniversary, Commander. We're just past the first half of a wonderful year, and I believe the trend will continue into the second half. May the Holy Iris grace you with its blessings. P.S.: I hope you enjoy our banquet."
60415.name: Richelieu's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60416.display: A card from Enterprise. It reads: "Another year, huh? Well, it's not JUST another year. I've seen new sights, made new friends, and formed new memories I'll treasure forever. I hope you have too, Commander. Happy anniversary."
60416.name: Enterprise's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60417.display: A card from Essex. It reads: "Happy anniversary, Commander! Whenever this time of year comes around, I'm always reminded of what a pleasure and honor it is to be at this port. Thank you for all you do for us. Also, if you have time later, will you drop by and test a lemonade cocktail recipe I've been working on?"
60417.name: Essex's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60418.display: A card from Belfast. It reads: "I wish you a happy anniversary, Master. Her Majesty requested that I deliver you a bottle of some our finest aged wine. At the risk of sounding brazen, would you like to share a glass with your humble maid?"
60418.name: Belfast's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60419.display: A card from Formidable. It reads: "Happy anniversary, Commander. I've been thinking – the classical music we play at our tea parties is fine and all, but don't you want to experience something new? I propose a private tea party between you and me. You bring the tea set, and I'll bring the rock records."
60419.name: Formidable's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60420.display: A card from Amagi. It reads: "Every anniversary is precious to me. It's a time to reminisce on fond memories, reconnect with old friends, and celebrate all the progress we've made. This one is no different, and I'm glad to be a part of it. Here is to your good health, Commander."
60420.name: Amagi's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60421.display: A card from Avrora. It reads: "Here we are again, Commander. Happy anniversary! What are your highlights of the year thus far? I hope you've met new people, sung good songs, and enjoyed some fine spirits. If you ever need a drinking buddy, you know where to find me!"
60421.name: Avrora's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60422.display: A card from Zara. It reads: "Hey, Commander. What a hot summer it's been, am I right? Wish I could wear something less... formal to the celebrations, but you know how the rules are. Here's to our anniversary, and to a good year!"
60422.name: Zara's Gift (5th Anniversary)

60435.display: A limited construction ticket for use during the "Upon the Shimmering Blue" event. Removed after the event ends.
60435.name: Shipbuilding Support Ticket

60450.display: A card from Kazagumo. It reads: "Happy New Year. If you want me to serve you for New Year's, then... I suppose I could."
60450.name: Kazagumo's Gift (New Year 2024)

60451.display: A card from Richelieu. It reads: "May the Holy Iris' blessings be with you into New Year's Day and beyond."
60451.name: Richelieu's Gift (New Year 2024)

60452.display: A card from U-101. It reads: "Come over and board Great Shark! I'll take you on a ride and we'll finish with the view of the first sunrise of the year!"
60452.name: U-101's Gift (New Year 2024)

60453.display: A card from Formidable. It reads: "My New Year's resolution is to moderate my food intake. May you have a graceful New Year, Commander."
60453.name: Formidable's Gift (New Year 2024)

60454.display: A card from Shangri-La. It reads: "The new year starts with a fresh notebook, waiting to be filled with daily happinesses. Happy New Year."
60454.name: Shangri-La's Gift (New Year 2024)

60455.display: A card from Zara. It reads: "I've got my scarf, I've got my bag, I've got you. What else do I need?"
60455.name: Zara's Gift (New Year 2024)

60456.display: A card from Tashkent. It reads: "Happy New Year, dear comrade. Why don't we toast with a hot drink?"
60456.name: Tashkent's Gift (New Year 2024)

60457.display: Use to receive an SR shipgirl of your choosing and a commemorative item.
60457.name: New Year's Invitation (2024)
